title: march 9: barbie makes her big debut
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the invention of the first Barbie doll and Barbie’s evolution from a blonde pinup in a swimsuit to a multicultural collection of doll-sized doctors, veterinarians, astronauts and presidents. Afterwards, she talks about Logic’s hit 2018 album, Bobby Tarantino II. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
